snippet.title: Broken Minds Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
So sorry for the repost — I had to remove the Astro Boy teapot from the game (and this trailer). In other news, Broken Minds (with Broken Egg included) is now on Game Jolt!

Play Broken Minds here!
https://lockedon.itch.io/broken-minds
https://gamejolt.com/games/brokenminds/331782

Get the soundtrack! https://oddtilltheend.bandcamp.com/album/broken-minds-original-soundtrack


On November 1st, 1992, in the quiet Yamagata prefecture in Japan, a strange incident has occurred. Noa Karada, an unusual 22-year-old living alone, has her house set on fire. The only suspect? A person wearing a rabbit mask. Or is it a goat mask? Only the Yamagata Private Detective Agency will be able to solve the mystery!

---

Mostly for posting full episodes of TEW!
